{"type":"message","id":"c12c688e","parentId":"10637e1b","timestamp":"2026-04-14T04:00:11.998Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:6f06e0b0-aa42-4280-8d04-8dcbf5f2d053 兆易创新午盘复盘+下午预测] 请执行兆易创新(603986)午盘复盘与下午预测任务：\n1) 首先执行 `bash ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/is_trading_day.sh` 检查今日是否为交易日，如非交易日则回复\"今日非A股交易日，跳过午盘复盘\"并结束任务；\n2) 读取 tracking/daily_prediction.json 的 am_session.prediction 内容；\n3) 通过腾讯财经API获取上午最新行情（开盘价、11:30收盘价、涨跌幅、成交量）；\n4) 对比早盘预测与实际走势，评估预测准确度；\n5) 生成午盘复盘报告（实际vs预测偏差分析）；\n6) 生成下午走势预测（含方向/区间/概率分布）；\n7) 更新 tracking/daily_prediction.json 的 am_session.review 和 pm_session.prediction。\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 12:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-14 04:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776139211996}}
